#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.i0.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.i0"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:1 of
msgid "Modified Bessel function of the first kind, order 0."
msgstr "第一类修正贝塞尔函数，阶数为 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:3 of
msgid ""
"Usually denoted :math:`I_0`.  This function does broadcast, but will "
"*not* \"up-cast\" int dtype arguments unless accompanied by at least one "
"float or complex dtype argument (see Raises below)."
msgstr ""
"通常表示为 :math:`I_0`。此函数支持广播，但不会将纯整数类型的参数“提升”"
"为更高精度，除非至少有一个参数是浮点型或复数类型（见下方 Raises）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0 of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:7 of
msgid "Argument of the Bessel function."
msgstr "贝塞尔函数的参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0 of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:10 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The modified Bessel function evaluated at each of the elements"
" of `x`."
msgstr "**out** -- 在 `x` 的每个元素处计算的第一类修正贝塞尔函数值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0 of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0 of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:13 of
msgid ""
"array cannot be safely cast to required type: If argument consists "
"exclusively of int dtypes."
msgstr "数组无法安全地转换为所需类型：如果参数完全由整数类型组成。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:15 of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.special.iv`, :py:obj:`scipy.special.ive`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:18 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:19 of
msgid ""
"We use the algorithm published by Clenshaw [1]_ and referenced by "
"Abramowitz and Stegun [2]_, for which the function domain is partitioned "
"into the two intervals [0,8] and (8,inf), and Chebyshev polynomial "
"expansions are employed in each interval. Relative error on the domain "
"[0,30] using IEEE arithmetic is documented [3]_ as having a peak of "
"5.8e-16 with an rms of 1.4e-16 (n = 30000)."
msgstr ""
"我们使用 Clenshaw [1]_ 发表并由 Abramowitz 和 Stegun [2]_ 引用的算法，该"
"算法将函数定义域划分为两个区间 [0,8] 和 (8,inf)，并在每个区间中使用切"
"比雪夫多项式展开。在 [0,30] 区间内使用 IEEE 算术计算所得的相对误差峰值为 "
"5.8e-16，均方根误差为 1.4e-16（n = 30000）[3]_。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:27 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:28 of
msgid ""
"C. W. Clenshaw, \"Chebyshev series for mathematical functions\", in "
"*National Physical Laboratory Mathematical Tables*, vol. 5, London: Her "
"Majesty's Stationery Office, 1962."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.i0.i0:31 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I. A. Stegun, *Handbook of Mathematical Functions*, "
"10th printing, New York: Dover, 1964, pp. 379. "
"http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/page_379.htm"
msgstr ""

